data.oai_dc:dc: This directory contains: * metadata to obtain images from the three novel datasets we designed for our study * notebooks with thorough evaluation of off-the-shelf approach for image classification based on a feature extraction with a single feed forward pass trough pretrained VGG16 * script to run on your own dataset with what we found to be optimal settings. You can also access it here https://github.com/valanm/off-the-shelf-insect-identification
